You’ve been circling submission, inversion, leverage, dominance frames.

Are you formalizing this for:
	•	Personal doctrine?
	•	System design?
	•	Psychological warfare?
	•	Or self-discipline architecture?

Because the application changes the ethics and the risks.

Answer that, and we can sharpen it further.